ts/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲過,所以淨係飲有氣"},{"pid":"898c7116d2610ecde9afe1777abd0500f0fe45f1","tid":282111,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:29:14.000Z","msg":"飲zero啦"},{"pid":"41b97c7b6192506b34b632d8a6e076c276ada3f9","tid":282111,"uid":120972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:29:23.000Z","msg":"可樂就冇 每日至少1罐啤酒就有"},{"pid":"a4409b05016ef5331ffc888cb77c74a958d39369","tid":282111,"uid":106169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:30:38.000Z","msg":"戒緊 好撚痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495ee788d2b1f980d5e6eafcc3be4843a9807051","tid":282111,"uid":38144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:31:29.000Z","msg":"y not zero"},{"pid":"6bf7997e8c09a9e9560a1b23fd4b7cd58f3348b7","tid":282111,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:32:46.000Z","msg":"&gt;23 好肥wO"},{"pid":"09eaf81738082c6e69d4ae29a47b408bcc6c588f","tid":282111,"uid":26003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:33:10.000Z","msg":"去旅行嗰陣會每日一支coke zero<br />\n<br />\n利申: 去緊旅行"},{"pid":"a924041e521d8b2ed78b3774dd7ef26d607f073f","tid":282111,"uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:35:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去旅行嗰陣會每日一支coke zero<br />\n<br />\n利申: 去緊旅行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncoke zero會飲到弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飲可樂都可以正常做運動減番出黎"},{"pid":"ac1fbbcf43fd822c4b81c879ccb6d2e595f92461","tid":282111,"uid":27447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:35:24.000Z","msg":"每日一罐 瘦撚 bmi正常"},{"pid":"c2fcd6ea02c5a8ee833eb7671312df0a317a2884","tid":282111,"uid":26003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去旅行嗰陣會每日一支coke zero<br />\n<br />\n利申: 去緊旅行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncoke zero會飲到弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飲可樂都可以正常做運動減番出黎</blockquote><br />\n去旅行先飲，<br />\n太熱，<br />\n平時冇飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3228b8a5cbfaf59eafd734e1db898ef0fcc48c68","tid":282111,"uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:37:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去旅行嗰陣會每日一支coke zero<br />\n<br />\n利申: 去緊旅行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncoke zero會飲到弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飲可樂都可以正常做運動減番出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncoke zero有Aspartame<br />\n<br />\nAspartame<br />\n中文：阿斯巴甜（含苯丙氨酸），屬於一種代糖，經常使用在低糖飲料當中。一種約比蔗糖甜200倍的甜味劑，<span style=\"color: orange;\">代糖已經被認為成一種神經毒素，損害神經系統，故這些症狀主要與神經系統有關。一些常見的與代糖有關的症狀為頭痛，記憶力衰退，癲癇，視力消失，昏迷及腫瘤。</span>代糖更可使以下疾病加重或導致類似這些疾病的症狀，比如︰纖維性肌痛，多發性硬化，系統性紅斑狼瘡，多動症，糖尿病，老年性或早老性痴呆，慢性疲勞綜合症和憂鬱症。研究已證明代糖能釋放自由甲醇。長期甲醇的毒性可影響腦中的多巴胺系統而導致上癮。甲醇又稱木醇，占代糖的1/3，此物質己被劃為嚴重的代謝性毒物和麻醉劑。"},{"pid":"03cd42bfcf0c13b0983be8fc3090ae41bcbec2dc","tid":282111,"uid":51527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:48:28.000Z","msg":"日日都整罐ZERO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為怕肥先揀飲黑可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常做完大量運動果日我先敢飲紅可樂"},{"pid":"d3d7f0b5f5e82fa521b8567b1c607074098dcbb8","tid":282111,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:53:23.000Z","msg":"岩岩計左32.x<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2fa09093ff743a2eeca3313f343358086824ad","tid":282111,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T11:45:26.000Z","msg":"肥仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快d走呀"},{"pid":"038312f34bdc38dd2306cf65c7af2f2