>\n飲可樂都可以正常做運動減番出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncoke zero有Aspartame<br />\n<br />\nAspartame<br />\n中文：阿斯巴甜（含苯丙氨酸），屬於一種代糖，經常使用在低糖飲料當中。一種約比蔗糖甜200倍的甜味劑，<span style=\"color: orange;\">代糖已經被認為成一種神經毒素，損害神經系統，故這些症狀主要與神經系統有關。一些常見的與代糖有關的症狀為頭痛，記憶力衰退，癲癇，視力消失，昏迷及腫瘤。</span>代糖更可使以下疾病加重或導致類似這些疾病的症狀，比如︰纖維性肌痛，多發性硬化，系統性紅斑狼瘡，多動症，糖尿病，老年性或早老性痴呆，慢性疲勞綜合症和憂鬱症。研究已證明代糖能釋放自由甲醇。長期甲醇的毒性可影響腦中的多巴胺系統而導致上癮。甲醇又稱木醇，占代糖的1/3，此物質己被劃為嚴重的代謝性毒物和麻醉劑。</blockquote><br />\n美國食品藥品監督管理局FDA把阿斯巴甜描述為「研究最徹底的食品添加劑之一」，其安全性「毋庸置疑」[23]。有一些通過電子郵件傳播的網絡流言宣傳說阿斯巴甜可能引起多種疾病[16]，然而美國疾病控制與預防中心（Centers for Disease Control and Prevention，CDC）的調查顯示並沒有流行病學證據可以驗證阿斯巴甜能引起重大傷害或嚴重風險。[24]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nfrom wiki only"},{"pid":"248b178c56e559b38ce88c792a48dbaba4e1eb6e","tid":282111,"uid":65400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:05:32.000Z","msg":"我鐘意飲梳打水 冇味幾味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D氣走晒就勁難飲"},{"pid":"7a1e9df0d83787cd387305c6b1c47c14feac7d95","tid":282111,"uid":65400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:05:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我鐘意飲梳打水 冇味幾爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D氣走晒就勁難飲</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2d8ec5b4996424106b0729ca3840cae653186cc3","tid":282111,"uid":2017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:14:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/231430_ba9d501829b0c3c097a1a7e04c409bdd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F231430_ba9d501829b0c3c097a1a7e04c409bdd.jpg&h=e5ca23e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇BMI？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57106a2c50fd8b62cfde41320d218a0e8af2cc1","tid":282111,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去旅行嗰陣會每日一支coke zero<br />\n<br />\n利申: 去緊旅行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncoke zero會飲到弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飲可樂都可以正常做運動減番出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncoke zero有Aspartame<br />\n<br />\nAspartame<br />\n中文：阿斯巴甜（含苯丙氨酸），屬於一種代糖，經常使用在低糖飲料當中。一種約比蔗糖甜200倍的甜味劑，<span style=\"color: orange;\">代糖已經被認為成一種神經毒素，損害神經系統，故這些症狀主要與神經系統有關。一些常見的與代糖有關的症狀為頭痛，記憶力衰退，癲癇，視力消失，昏迷及腫瘤。</span>代糖更可使以下疾病加重或導致類似這些疾病的症狀，比如︰纖維性肌痛，多發性硬化，系統性紅斑狼瘡，多動症，糖尿病，老年性或早老性痴呆，慢性疲勞綜合症和憂鬱症。研究已證明代糖能釋放自由甲醇。長期甲醇的毒性可影響腦中的多巴胺系統而導致上癮。甲醇又稱木醇，占代糖的1/3，此物質己被劃為嚴重的代謝性毒物和麻醉劑。</blockquote><br />\n美國食品藥品監督管理局FDA把阿斯巴甜描述為「研究最徹底的食品添加劑之一」，其安全性「毋庸置疑」[23]。有一些通過電子郵件傳播的網絡流言宣傳說阿斯巴甜可能引起多種疾病[16]，然而美國疾病控制與預防中心（Centers for Disease Control and Prevention，CDC）的調查顯示並沒有流行病學證據可以驗證阿斯巴甜能引起重大傷害或嚴重風險。[24]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nfrom wiki only</blockquote><br />\nFDA<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fda.gov/food/ingredientspackaginglabeling/foodadditivesingredients/ucm397725.htm#Aspartame\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Ffood%2Fingredientspackaginglabeling%2Ffoodadditivesingredients%2Fucm397725.htm%23Aspartame&d=zhzUYjFy93mj2Ai8xmLBgcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=57c299d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fda.gov/food/ingredientspackaginglabeling/foodadditivesingredients/ucm397725.htm#Aspartame</a><br />\n重點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Aspartame is one of the most exhaustively studied substances in the human food supply, with more than 100 studies supporting its safety.</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fda.gov/food/ingredientspackaginglabeling/foodadditivesingredients/ucm208580.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Ffood%2Fingredientspackaginglabeling%2Ffoodadditivesingredients%2Fucm208580.htm&d=zhzUYjFy93mj2Ai8xmLBgcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=7dfe4ea1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fda.gov/food/ingredientspackaginglabeling/foodadditivesingredients/ucm208580.htm</a><br />\n重點<br />\nFDA has completed its review concerning the long-term carcinogenicity study of aspartame entitled, &quot;Long-Term Carcinogenicity Bioassays to Evaluate the Potential Biological Effects, in Particular Carcinogenic, of Aspartame Administered in Feed to Sprague-Dawley Rats,&quot; conducted by the European Ramazzini Foundation (ERF), located in Bologna, Italy. <span style=\"color: red;\">FDA reviewed the study data made available to them by ERF and finds that it does not support ERF's conclusion that aspartame is a carcinogen. Additionally, these data do not provide evidence to alter FDA's conclusion that the use of aspartame is safe.</span><br />\n<br />\nAmerican Cancer Society<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cancer.org/cancer/cancer-causes/aspartame.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cancer.org%2Fcancer%2Fcancer-causes%2Faspartame.html&d=zhzUYjFy93mj2Ai8xmLBgcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=c42a4ff0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cancer.org/cancer/cancer-causes/aspartame.html</a><br />\n重點<br />\nClaims have been made that aspartame is related to health effects ranging from mild problems such as headache, dizziness, digestive symptoms, and changes in mood, to more serious health issues such as Alzheimer disease, birth defects, diabetes, Gulf War syndrome, attention deficit disorders, Parkinson disease, lupus, multiple sclerosis, and seizures. <span style=\"color: red;\">However, studies done to date have not found any consistent evidence of harm.</span>"},{"pid":"f1ee3b3a105096268f14bf7c75fe15d6b50614ab","tid":282111,"uid":42402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:08:38.000Z","msg":"我一日至少兩罐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ec8893b6d260989b582e3d466515b18792f323","tid":282111,"uid":16373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:12:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講下你地身體狀況如何<br />\n我:有肚腩,BMI&gt;23,冇糖尿病,夏天冇可樂生存唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全盛時期一星期七日每日五罐<br />\n同你差唔多"},{"pid":"a0f243250eb4cb6d67e195202a9faad25e1d9534","tid":282111,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:31:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去旅行嗰陣會每日一支coke zero<br />\n<br />\n利申: 去緊旅行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncoke zero會飲到弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飲可樂都可以正常做運動減番出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncoke zero有Aspartame<br />\n<br />\nAspartame<br />\n中文：阿斯巴甜（含苯丙氨酸），屬於一種代糖，經常使用在低糖飲料當中。一種約比蔗糖甜200倍的甜味劑，<span style=\"color: orange;\">代糖已經被認為成一種神經毒素，損害神經系統，故這些症狀主要與神經系統有關。一些常見的與代糖有關的症狀為頭痛，記憶力衰退，癲癇，視力消失，昏迷及腫瘤。</span>代糖更可使以下疾病加重或導致類似這些疾病的症狀，比如︰纖維性肌痛，多發性硬化，系統性紅斑狼瘡，多動症，糖尿病，老年性或早老性痴呆，慢性疲勞綜合症和憂鬱症。研究已證明代糖能釋放自由甲醇。長期甲醇的毒性可影響腦中的多巴胺系統而導致上癮。甲醇又稱木醇，占代糖的1/3，此物質己被劃為嚴重的代謝性毒物和麻醉劑。</blockquote><br />\n美國食品藥品監督管理局FDA把阿斯巴甜描述為「研究最徹底的食品添加劑之一」，其安全性「毋庸置疑」[23]。有一些通過電子郵件傳播的網絡流言宣傳說阿斯巴甜可能引起多種疾病[16]，然而美國疾病控制與預防中心（Centers for Disease Control and Prevention，CDC）的調查顯示並沒有流行病學證據可以驗證阿斯巴甜能引起重大傷害或嚴重風險。[24]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nfrom wiki only</blockquote><br />\n條友都onlun9<br />\n網上垃圾post走去quote<br />\nnature science呢d執7佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8efbc53c0674a89791e95ac217d2ce8db5a829ad","tid":282111,"uid":72688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:33:02.000Z","msg":"上年返長短周早餐日日食吉野家+百事走冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3d6de0e07358ec1a75ff1b2f98525f883c2975","tid":282111,"uid":72688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上年返長短周早餐日日食吉野家+百事走冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有肥仔波同肚腩BMI正常"},{"pid":"8e6e6eb71115133d7b4ac4e342b2d3300fd9674e","tid":282111,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:37:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試晒全球唔同國家嘅可樂未？有無分別？<br />\n<br />\n剩係知大陸zero好撚難飲</blockquote><br />\n日本個隻唔夠氣又唔夠(那)喉</blockquote><br />\n日本d氣last得耐d喎<br />\n香港果d極速就無晒"},{"pid":"667469118c4bb41dded3c9bcacbe5acfd8a79d9e","tid":282111,"uid":99102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:43:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bce72fcf1abf89a22607228c8742054b3bb20c7e","tid":282111,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:51:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身每日飲原味可樂轉飲coke zero後瘦左幾廿磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa4a072b9b4cef15f86e5e371024e183d6158b9","tid":282111,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T17:17:33.000Z","msg":"之前日日飲一樽（7仔膠樽/一公升），有時飲大樽有時飲細樽<br />\n嗰排狂生暗瘡又心跳加速又頭痛<br />\n之後停咗唔飲汽水就冇事"},{"pid":"8acdb4b2cb7acb51ebad70e6b7ebea24c68560e4","tid":282111,"uid":81609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T17:28:23.000Z","msg":"每日一罐黑可樂<br />\n<br />\nBMI &gt;30"},{"pid":"3a673fe853f145b78bd179835cc7ebfb9d30d0c0","tid":282111,"uid":50253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:38:20.000Z","msg":"維持左兩年<br />\nbmi乜乜乜冇變過<br />\n都係一米7幾140磅<br />\n唔覺有咩問題<br />\n最癲個陣可樂當水飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b660fca660b345c6ca75fc290cf464efb907f9","tid":282111,"uid":9543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:52:51.000Z","msg":"鍾意飲coke lite <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n周圍都無賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有都係濕鳩檸檬味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161f125e54b628e7f8b528539c3fe95616f5f08c","tid":282111,"uid":4545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":